nodes.text: Spiced Cannok Canapes was a flavorful type of canapé developed by Napo Popotis, a chef from the planet Onderon. Like most of Popotis's most famous creations, the canapés were made from a local animal—in this case the cannok, which was native to Onderon's moon Dxun.
Spiced Cannok Canapes were mentioned in the "Delicacies from the Demon Moon" Codex entry in Onslaught, a 2019 Digital Expansion for the video game Star Wars: The Old Republic.
